title: CreativeLIVE - Fast Start Canon 70D with John Greengo
description:
Fast Start Canon 70D with John Greengo

Ready to make the most of your Canon 70D? Join expert photographer John Greengo for a fast-track introduction to taking full advantage of your camera's features. John will cover how to navigate and set up your camera's menus and guide you through its buttons, dials, and features. You'll learn how to take full advantage of your camera's super-fast live view focusing. You'll also learn how to optimize your camera for sports and other high-motion photography. John will also cover the power of your camera's high-resolution sensors and settings and help you get them attuned to your shooting style so you get the picture you want, every time. This course will have you using your Canon 70D like a pro in no time -- no complicated manuals required.
